title: TSR Super Heroes
description:
*This will be my very first upload so if there is any issue, please let me know and I will try to rectify the problem quickly*

This is one of the most comprehensive sets of TSR Marvel Super Heroes files that you will find on the net currently. 

If anyone else has better/additional files that they wish to share with the rest of the community, please let me know and I will update the torrent accordingly.

There have been many people that have added to this file over the years and I would like to say thank you, for letting me share it with the rest of the community.

Nuff said!
